:"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d3d9/022e/22571_mini.png?m=1401716860"},{"id":803103,"node":"生活","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","description":"<p>标题可能说得不太清楚，就是想在衣着搭配上或者发型上改进一下，想要改掉刻板的直男形象</p>\n<p>最近接触异性的机会较多，她们反馈的结果就是觉得我颜值尚可，就是穿着过于普通呆板。说是有很大改进空间，不知道是不是骗我 /笑哭</p>\n<p>日常我最常见的搭配是牛仔裤+纯色 T 恤，她们建议我可以专门做个发型（碎盖头），再买个这几年流行的遮阳帽（渔夫帽）。</p>\n<p>这种搭配给我的第一感觉是太 fashion 了（可能是自己太土了 QAQ ），直男程序员（不过应该很快就不做程序员了）一下子改成这个设定坐地铁会不会 hold 不住 2333 </p>\n<p>但是自己确实想要做出一些改变，试试也未尝不可</p>\n<p>V 友们有没有尝试过类似的自我改造，有没有好的建议，提前感谢</p>\n<p>我在网上找了样张，如下</p>\n<p><img alt=\"https://files.catbox.moe/xy72or.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/xy72or.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"https://files.catbox.moe/f9kdqb.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/f9kdqb.jpg\"/></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/803103","replies":33,"created_ts":1632148197,"created":"22:29:57","title":"想要变得酷酷的，有没有什么快捷的办法？","author":"manami","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/manami","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9166/4abd/453453_mini.png?m=1632145903"},{"id":803091,"node":"北京","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/beijing","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1f0e/3dad/19_mini.png?m=1588235467","description":"<ul>\n<li>房租没有深圳高？</li>\n<li>平均工资不低？</li>\n<li>千年古城？</li>\n<li>多元融合？</li>\n<li>宇宙的中心？</li>\n<li>社区友好？</li>\n<li>Others?</li>\n</ul>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/803091","replies":33,"created_ts":1632144418,"created":"21:26:58","title":"喜欢北京，需要什么理由？","author":"iClass","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/iClass","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/57a0/da87/543932_mini.png?m=1630259926"},{"id":803078,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1631867212","description":"<p>公司的福利给每人报销 5000 的学习基金，必须是学习和培训的发票才能报销。</p>\n<p>自己一直想提高英语，去 EF 看了看，一直强调高端至少要 1 万大几，坚持这个预算时售课就有点阴阳怪气了。</p>\n<p>请各位大佬推荐在这个预算范围的培训，英语最好，其他也可接受。</p>\n<p>坐标广州。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/803078","replies":33,"created_ts":1632138304,"created":"19:45:04","title":"公司给报销 5000 学习基金，请推荐","author":"zherrrrrrrr","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/zherrrrrrrr","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/18e6197b2e70293f85f48f20f93c7ec1?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":803019,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1629391393","description":"<p>今天签收 iPad，顺丰快递小哥居然要了我的 sfz，放在快递单旁边拍照。我回想了一下之前签收 mac 的时候好像也只是要求查看一下证件，并没有拍照。签收其他顺丰快递的时候更是连证件都没要过。百度了一下，基本都是说首次寄件需要证件。</p>\n<p>当时我看快递员拍完照好像是发到了微信上，不知道是发到了他们的群里还是自己的文件传输助手。我瞬间背后一凉，心想他不会拿我证件搞什么违法乱纪的事情吧。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/803019","replies":33,"created_ts":1632104344,"created":"10:19:04","title":"顺丰收件还需要拍证件么？","author":"jamme","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/jamme","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4ec7/2727/199115_mini.png?m=1531290444"},{"id":803023,"node":"优惠信息","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/deals","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/8d31/7bdc/747_mini.png?m=1523201604","description":"<p>From Weibo: 回收宝联合 @努比亚手机 发起「 iPhone 充电器免费换新」活动，9.19-9.23 ，在 [努比亚手机 or 回收宝] 双微，回复\"以旧换新\"，预约报名后到指定回收宝门店，即有机会免费换新 [努比亚小方糖充电器小黄人联名版] ！ <img alt=\"QQ 截图 20210920110638.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/09/20/l9X6AQNKmsiW1ZF.png\"/></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/803023","replies":32,"created_ts":1632107101,"created":"11:05:01","title":"北上广深的兄弟们可以用旧的 iPhone 充电器可以免费换努比亚的小黄人充电器了","author":"zhoudaiyu","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/zhoudaiyu","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b75f/9ee0/163414_mini.png?m=1574570790"},{"id":803009,"node":"互联网","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/internet","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navat