","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/um1ng","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/13b9/ffe9/153198_mini.png?m=1631943761"},{"id":803032,"node":"硬件","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/hardware","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_mini.png?m=1630576655","description":"<div>\n<p>局域网两台机器直连，距离就 1 米，求推荐两块网兆网卡，最好二手能用就行，经济实惠的，性价比高的，东哥家看了下好贵。</p>\n</div>","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/803032","replies":19,"created_ts":1632114012,"created":"13:00:12","title":"求推荐万兆网卡","author":"shovo","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/shovo","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/429d/cbcb/446833_mini.png?m=1571070985"},{"id":803026,"node":"Linux","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/linux","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_mini.png?m=1620106980","description":"UI 几乎是照着 Windows11 一顿抄,感觉就是拿别的桌面环境改的。<br /><br />竟然还有收费版，20 刀<br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.windowsfx.org/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://www.windowsfx.org/</a>","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/803026","replies":19,"created_ts":1632110467,"created":"12:01:07","title":"偶然看到的一个 Linux 发行版， WindowsFx","author":"levima","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/levima","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c583/9f09/500248_mini.png?m=1620722173"}]